Components
----------
1. 2 XBee S1
2. 1 XBee Explorer Regulated <https://www.sparkfun.com/products/9132> 
3. 1 XBee Explorer USB <https://www.sparkfun.com/products/8687>



How to configure an XBee connected to PC via an XBee Explorer USB
------------------------------------------------------------------
> sudo python xbeeterm.py 115200
xbee% serial /dev/ttyUSB0
Opening serial port: /dev/ttyUSB0
xbee% +++
OK
xbee% AT
OK
xbee% ATID
1111
xbee% ATMY
11
xbee% ATDL
10
xbee% ATBD
7
xbee% ATBD 5
OK
xbee% ATWR
OK
xbee% exit



